    <item>
      <title>식집사님들 필독! 폭염에도 끄떡없는 반려식물 여름나기 비법은?</title>
      <link>https://plantmaru.com/posts/calendar/2025-07-06-summerplantsurvivalguide/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Jul 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>plantmaru@plantmaru.com (plantmaru)</author>
      <guid>https://plantmaru.com/posts/calendar/2025-07-06-summerplantsurvivalguide/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;식집사님들 필독! 폭염에도 끄떡없는 반려식물 여름나기 비법은? 🌿☀️ 
    &lt;div id=&#34;식집사님들-필독-폭염에도-끄떡없는-반려식물-여름나기-비법은&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
